Kenya Wine Agencies Limited recently celebrated Viceroy Brandy’s new stage, termed “a blend of the best”, through a customer event held at the Tav Irish Pub on Waiyaki Way. The event was attended by the Viceroy global brand manager Renato Santana, Kwal managing director Lina Githuka as well as Viceroy consumers. Santana took consumers through the journey that Viceroy has taken for the last 150 years, and how best to consume it. 